* `x = X / Z^2 = n*g / sqrt(d*g)^2 = n*g / (d*g) = n/d = x`
* `y = Y / Z^2 = g^2 / sqrt(d*g)^3 = (n^3 + B*d^3)^2 / sqrt(d^3) / (n^3 + B*d^3)^1.5 = sqrt(n^3 + B*d^3) / sqrt(d^3) = sqrt(n^3/d^3 + B) = y`

